<div class="preview {$background}">
<p><strong><a href="/scp-1948-j">SCP-1948-J</a></strong><br />
<em>最新评论：</em> <strong><tt>Soviet-Zhang</tt></strong> <em>于</em> <strong><tt><span class="odate time_1555916777 format_%25D%20%25H%3A%25M">22 Apr 2019 07:06</span></tt></strong><br />
<em>最新编辑：</em> <strong><tt>6TsebEht</tt></strong> <em>于</em> <strong><tt><span class="odate time_1567953246 format_%25D%20%25H%3A%25M">08 Sep 2019 14:34</span></tt></strong></p>
